headline: Samsung Electronics Partners With Electronic Arts and Xbox To Bring EA SPORTS FC 25 to Samsung Gaming Hub
summary: Samsung TV and monitor owners can now play EA SPORTS FC 25 via the Xbox app.New players with eligible Samsung TVs and monitors can get two months of Xbox Game Pass UltimateSamsung Electronics today...

headline: 2 Nasdaq 100 Stocks to Target This Week and 1 to Question
summary: While the Nasdaq 100 (^NDX) is filled with cutting-edge technology and consumer companies, not all are on solid footing. Some are dealing with declining demand, high costs, or regulatory pressures that could limit future upside.
